        <p class="parrafo col-8 col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-6 col-sm-8">Backlit, name that this project receives, was my end-of-degree project in 2020. It was extremely challenging because, apart from a class I took that very same year that was relatively related to journlaism and data visualization, I had no other kind of experience. Anyway, I really wanted to start this project and I could bring it to an end thanks to all the help received and hours and hours of research and hard work. That is how I could create this report, whose main objective was to show all those small towns in Spain as something more than a number, as we usually see in media.
          <i>The actual version is a result of a revision process that took place in March 2022.</i></p>
