        <h3 class="titulo_seccion mt-4">Technologies used</h3>
      </div>    
        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
        <p class="parrafo col-8 col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-6 col-sm-8">For the layout HTML and CSS were used. Besides that, when looking from top to bottom, both videos (at the beginning and end of the page) were editied with Adobe Premiere. All maps appearing in the videos were created with QGIS and exported as images. The map under the header was also created with QGIS, although it was exported to HTML format with QGIS’s plugging qgis2web. The drop-down menu on top of the maps was created by customizing a JS template. The bar graph was created with Adobe Illustrator’s chart tool and animted with Adobe After Effects. The scatterplot at the bottom was created with R’s library ggplot2, that also allows for interactivity to be applied to graphs.</p>
        </div>
